logicalColumns.name: Firm Status
logicalColumns.description:
'Packed'/'Not Firm'/'Contents Firm'

Formula:

CASE "SSYS"."Dim - Delivery"."Planned Flag" 
WHEN 'N' THEN
CASE  WHEN "SSYS"."Dim - Delivery"."Attribute3"='Y' THEN 'Packed'
ELSE 'Not Firm'
END
WHEN 'Y' THEN 'Contents Firm'
END

logicalExpression.expressionTemplate: CASE %1 WHEN 'N' THEN  CASE  WHEN %2 = 'Y' THEN 'Packed' ELSE 'Not Firm' END  WHEN 'Y' THEN 'Contents Firm' END
